1. Make grasping motions at chest level four times.
2. With your fists at your chest level, perform four complete flapping motions 
	with your elbows.
3. Sway your hips from side to side four times (two to each side), moving your 
	pelvis closer to the ground as you do.
4. As you are rise to a standing position, clap four times.
5. Repeat these steps until the swing portion of the song begins. Then, swing 
	either alone, with a partner, or with a large group of software 
	engineers and lawyers.
6. Repeat from beginning until the song is complete.
